summary:
I am an experienced English Teacher with a demonstrated history of working in ELT industry. Skilled in English as a Second Language (ESL), Internet Savvy, Coaching, Lecturing, and Editing. Strong education professional with a Trinity DipTESOL and a Cambridge CELTA certificate and BA English from the University of Cape Town. I have also developed my own Moodle language platform for dedicated assistance to language learners from all over the globe. 
I am currently working on developing my skills as an EAP/ESP teacher and course developer.
